  "explanation": "Sort words lexicographically. Build a set of valid words starting from empty string.",
  "answer": "def longestWord(words):\n    words.sort()\n    valid, res = {\"\"}, \"\"\n    for w in words:\n        if w[:-1] in valid:\n            valid.add(w)\n            if len(w) > len(res): res = w\n    return res",
